docker, kubernetes and jenkins course
pre-requisite:
1. basics of java language, how to run java application
2. how to deploy an java application on a servlet container environment
3. basics of linux operating system and package managers
apt, yum, dpkg and other package management tools
4. optionally good to have shellscripting knowledge
5. basics of networking and protocols

system requirements:-
--------------------------------
windows 10 operating system
i3/i5/i7 processor or ryzen5 series
ram: 8gb
hdd/ssd: 100 gb freespace

