---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
docker: (15-20 days)
1. what is containerization technology, why do we need to use it
2. compare virtualization with containerization technology and discuss the benefits and drawbacks of each of them
3. The architecture of docker
4. docker workflow
5. docker layer images
6. docker installation
7. docker CLI
8. how bake our own docker image (superior in docker) (docker files)
		- docker directives (image instructions and container instructions)
9. docker networking
10. docker container lifecycle
11. docker volumes
12. docker inspect
13. docker mounts
14. docker container registry

kubernetes (k8s) [15 - 20 days]
1. what is kubernetes cluster manager why do we need it
2. kubernetes architecture
3. setup an kubernetes cluster using
	1. minikube
	2. standalone kubernetes cluster setup (kubeadm)
4. kubectl
5. kubeproxy
6. kubernetes objects
	1. pod
	2. deployment
	3. service
	4. nodes
	5. load balancer
7. kubeconfig
8. kubernetes networking options
9. aws kubernetes service (eks)
10. kubernetes config maps
11. kubernetes secrets

Jenkins [7-10 days]
1. Introduction to  Jenkins
2. Why continous integration
3. Jenkins setup and configure jenkins plugins
4. integrate jenkins with github
5. Jenkins administration
	1. users
	2. slaves
	3. manage plugins
6. working with jenkins free style project
7. understand jenkins pipelines
	1. declarative pipelines (dsl)
	2. scripted pipelines (requires groovy scripting)
8. configuring maven, docker plugins using jenkins
